The evidence with the title 'PunditFact: two claims that are definitely not true about Ebola ... ' says Aug 13, 2014  ... Bloggers also are behind a claim that " president (Barack) Obama signed an executive order mandating the detention of Americans who show signs of ' respiratory illness . ' " ... Also , the updated order does not "mandate" the apprehension and detention of people who show signs of respiratory illness . 
